    #main
      section.one.dark.cover#top
        .container
          header
            h2.alt Hi! I'm #[strong Lubien], a Computer Science student and Web Developer.
            p Currently I'm on a internship at #[a(href="https://github.com/projeto-spider/", alt="Projeto Spider") @projeto-spider] and I'm always contributing to the #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien", alt="Lubien profile at GitHub") Open Source].

          footer
            a.button.scrolly(href="#portfolio") Portfolio

      section.two#portfolio
        .container
          header
            h2 Portfolio

          p Bachelor course student in Computer Science at the Federal University of Pará, I have as hobby web development. Overall, I create systems that could make my life easier. Since I enjoy the process of making websites, I've been learning tools to make possible to abstract my ideas in a digital being.

          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/bookmarker", alt="Bookmarker", target="_blank") Bookmarker] Export Google Chrome bookmarks into markdown files.
          p.align-left #[a(href="roundabot-telegram", alt="RoundaBot", target="_blank") RoundaBot] Bot for JoJo Bizarre Adventures fans who'd like to finish their conversations JoJo-like.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/popura", alt="Popura", target="_blank") Popura] NodeJS wrapper for MyAnimeList API.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/popura", alt="Popura CLI", target="_blank") Popura CLI] CLI for NodeJS's popura package.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/fbmosaic", alt="Facebook Mosaic", target="_blank") Facebook Mosaic] https://github.com/lubien/fbmosaic
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/tosxp", alt="Tree of Savior XP Cards Calculator", target="_blank") Tree of Savior XP Cards Calculator] Tree of Savior XP calculator.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/easy-parser", alt="easy-parser", target="_blank") easy-parser] SimpleHTMLDOM abstraction.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/jay-ess/restinga-node", alt="Restinga Node", target="_blank") Restinga Node] REST API abstraction layer to easily consume data. Based on artesaos/restinga.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/koa-react-redux-universal-boilerplate", alt="koa-react-redux-universal-boilerplate", target="_blank") koa-react-redux-universal-boilerplate] A fullstack Koa + React + Redux Universal Boilerplate to speed up your development process.
          p.align-left #[a(href="https://github.com/lubien/flat-mal", alt="Flat MyAnimeList", target="_blank") Flat MyAnimeList] A design for myanimelist.net lists.

      section.three#about
        .container
          header
            h2 About Me

          a.image.featured(href="#")
            img(src="images/banner2.jpg")

          p I'm Computer Science student that loves web development and learning new programming languages and everything that could make me a better developer.

          p Right now, as of 2016 October 23, I'm focusing on learn Elixir since thats a lovely language to do server side stuff.

          p My other known languages are JavaScript (my main at the moment) and PHP yet I know a little bit about Haskell, Elm, Python  and C as there where situations where I needed them.

          p Currently, my web development stack consist of Koa for the backend, any popular SQL database and ReactJS with Redux for the front-end. Also I've already experienced making applications with ElectronJS, Cordova and MongoDB.

